metadata.description: The vision of JI capital is to become the greatest Web3(not only focus on crypto but also nfts or any other fields that form the basis of the crypto world) ecosystem in the world, one that is powered by a thriving community of creators, investors, alpha hunters and even ventures capital who sit at the intersection of JI DAO, JI Tools, and JI Ventures.
